title: FZ9- Timeshift - Legacy of The Cold War v1.3.2 Android .APK
description:
Spend Mac, a lost American soldier, in his mission to destroy the terrorist organization AS.  Collect rifles, machine guns and rocket launchers to destroy enemies with the effect of "frozen time".  Carefully watch, aim and BA-BACH!  In the game & quot; FZ9: Time shift & quot;  There are your favorite weapons - Glock, AK-47, M4A1 - and a detailed upgrade system that gives you the opportunity to create your own unique weapon in your arsenal.  In addition to the story missions, take on new challenges in three other game modes: compete with other players in the PVP, collect valuable resources in repetitive missions and be prepared to marvel at the unique tests in the weekly trials.  Start the execution of desperate missions - and protect the world from terrorists! 
MAIN CHARACTERISTICS

Shoot from a huge number of guns so beloved by shooters. 
Learn a detailed upgrade system with elements of role-playing game. 
Challenge yourself in several game modes. 
* IMPORTANT *  FZ9: Timeshift to work in the mode requires at least 1.5 GB of RAM.  The game requires an Internet connection
